<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><!-- wp:html --><li>Speakers get a free ticket to WordCamp and an invitation to a VIP dinner prior to the event, but are not otherwise compensated.</li><!-- /wp:html --><!-- wp:html --><li>Sessions cannot be sales pitches for your product or services.</li><!-- /wp:html --><!-- wp:html --><li>Each session will be recorded and submitted to <a href="https://wordpress.tv/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">WordPress.tv</a>, so you’ll need to sign an A/V release form.</li><!-- /wp:html --><!-- wp:html --><li>We will request presentation slides for review a few weeks before WordCamp. Make sure you can meet that deadline.</li><!-- /wp:html --></ul>
